OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778666815
OL,3,CWoman born without lower right arm
OL,4,C'excluded' from Kent Police job
OL,6,FITV News Meridian's Sarah Saunders has
OL,7,Fbeen speaking to Keira Semple
OL,9,FA woman from Ashford who was born
OL,10,Fwithout a lower right arm says she is
OL,11,Fbeing excluded from job opportunities,
OL,12,Fincluding driving for Kent Police,
OL,13,Fbecause of inability to get a certain
OL,14,Ftype of driving licence.
OL,16,FKeira Semple has been behind the wheel
OL,17,Fsince she was 17 but says adverts from
OL,18,Fpotential employers often require a
OL,19,Fmanual driving licence, which rules
OL,20,Fher out from applying.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
