OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778666815
OL,3,CWoman born without lower right arm
OL,4,C'excluded' from Kent Police job
OL,6,FKeira has an adapted steering wheel
OL,7,Fand is looking to have this removed as
OL,8,Fbelieves she could drive comfortably.
OL,10,FThe 19-year old said she finds a
OL,11,Fmanual driving licence is
OL,12,Fautomatically listed as a standard
OL,13,Frequirement in many job descriptions,
OL,14,Feven where automatic or adapted
OL,15,Fvehicles could be used and so doesn't
OL,16,Fsee a reason why she shouldn't be able
OL,17,Fto apply for certain roles.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778666815
OL,3,CWoman born without lower right arm
OL,4,C'excluded' from Kent Police job
OL,6,F"It's really frustrating because I see
OL,7,Fa job I really want to do or it sounds
OL,8,Freally interesting and I'm unable to
OL,9,Fdo it.
OL,11,F"It's frustrating because people like
OL,12,Fme are unable to get that manual
OL,13,Flicence so we are automatically
OL,14,Fdisqualified - especially when I
OL,15,Fbelieve I can do the job very well.
OL,17,FEven though she's facing barriers, the
OL,18,F19-year old does currently holds a job
OL,19,Fand produces coaching videos online,
OL,20,Fbut she would like to do a job giving
OL,21,Fback to the community.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778666815
OL,3,CWoman born without lower right arm
OL,4,C'excluded' from Kent Police job
OL,6,FKeira said, "I looked at Kent Police.
OL,7,FI'm unable to do that because of an
OL,8,Fautomatic licence because they require
OL,9,Fa full UK driving licence, whereas
OL,10,FThames Valley Police can have either
OL,11,For - so a manual licence of an
OL,12,Fautomatic one. automatic or manual
OL,13,Flicense.
OL,15,F"I think it is outdated because in
OL,16,F2026 most cars are made to be
OL,17,Fautomatic, so I think they need to
OL,18,Fupdate the rules."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778666815
OL,3,CWoman born without lower right arm
OL,4,C'excluded' from Kent Police job
OL,6,FKent Police said, "All officers
OL,7,Fresponding to urgent calls for
OL,8,Fassistance may need to use a manual
OL,9,Fpatrol car if that is the only one
OL,10,Favailable.
OL,12,F"It is this commitment to protecting
OL,13,Fpeople from harm 24/7 that compels us
OL,14,Fto require applicants for the post of
OL,15,Fconstable to hold a full UK licence.
OL,17,F"There are other police staff and
OL,18,Fvolunteer roles within Kent Police
OL,19,Fwhich do not have this mandatory
OL,20,Frequirement. "
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
