PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778666815
OL,3,CWoman born without lower right arm
OL,4,C'excluded' from Kent Police job
OL,6,FThe disability charity Scope says
OL,7,Fpeople with disabilities applying for
OL,8,Fwork should contact the employer
OL,9,Fdirect,
OL,11,FEmployment team manager Guy Chaudoir
OL,12,Fsaid,"I think what some people do
OL,13,Fencounter is this manual licence only
OL,14,For must be a car drive.
OL,16,F"My best piece of advice would be to
OL,17,Fget in touch with the employer and
OL,18,Fcheck this is essential or are there
OL,19,Freasonable adjustments they could make
OL,20,Fto be able to fulfil that job."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
